### Layer 2 — `--c-*` Semantic Aliases

Add this block **after** the shadcn tokens in the same `:root`. These aliases consume shadcn tokens — they hold no raw values of their own. Because they reference `var(--shadcn-token)`, they automatically update when `.dark` overrides the base tokens.

```css
:root {
  /* ── Surfaces ── */
  --c-bg:          var(--sidebar);           /* page canvas */
  --c-card:        var(--card);
  --c-subtle:      var(--muted);             /* tag bg, qa-bar, client row fills */

  /* ── Text ── */
  --c-text:        var(--foreground);
  --c-muted:       var(--muted-foreground);

  /* ── Brand ── */
  --c-green:       var(--primary);
  --c-green-lt:    oklch(from var(--primary) calc(l + 0.35) calc(c - 0.08) h);
  --c-green-hover: oklch(from var(--primary) calc(l - 0.08) c h);

  /* ── Status ── */
  --c-amber:       var(--status-review);
  --c-red:         var(--destructive);

  /* ── Structure ── */
  --c-border:      var(--border);

  /* ── Shadows ── */
  --c-shadow:      0 1px 3px oklch(0 0 0 / 7%), 0 1px 2px oklch(0 0 0 / 4%);
  --c-shadow-md:   0 4px 16px oklch(0 0 0 / 8%);

  /* ── Typography ── */
  --font-sans:     'Outfit', sans-serif;
  --font-serif:    'Fraunces', serif;
  --font-mono:     'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
}
```

> **Note on `--c-green-lt` and `--c-green-hover`:** These use relative `oklch()` color syntax to derive tints/shades directly from `--primary`. This means they automatically adapt when `--primary` changes in `.dark` mode. If your target browser doesn't support relative color syntax yet, define them as literal `oklch()` values in both `:root` and `.dark` instead:
> ```css
> /* Light */  --c-green-lt:    oklch(0.95 0.05 163);
> /* Light */  --c-green-hover: oklch(0.52 0.13 163);
> /* Dark  */  --c-green-lt:    oklch(0.25 0.05 163);
> /* Dark  */  --c-green-hover: oklch(0.78 0.15 162);
> ```

---

### Complete Token Map

| `--c-*` alias | Resolves via | shadcn source token |
|---|---|---|
| `--c-bg` | `var(--sidebar)` | `--sidebar` |
| `--c-card` | `var(--card)` | `--card` |
| `--c-subtle` | `var(--muted)` | `--muted` / `--accent` / `--secondary` |
| `--c-text` | `var(--foreground)` | `--foreground` |
| `--c-muted` | `var(--muted-foreground)` | `--muted-foreground` |
| `--c-green` | `var(--primary)` | `--primary` |
| `--c-green-lt` | derived from `--primary` | `--primary` |
| `--c-green-hover` | derived from `--primary` | `--primary` |
| `--c-amber` | `var(--status-review)` | supplemental |
| `--c-red` | `var(--destructive)` | `--destructive` |
| `--c-border` | `var(--border)` | `--border` |

