## 3. Layout & Spacing

### Page Structure
```
┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│  Header  (padding: 28px 32px 0)                 │
│  Tabs    (padding: 0 32px)                       │
│  Content (padding: 24px 32px 0)                  │
│  ┌──────────────────────────────────────────┐   │
│  │  KPI Row  (4-col grid, gap: 12px)        │   │
│  ├─────────────────────┬────────────────────┤   │
│  │  Left col  (60fr)   │  Right col (40fr)  │   │
│  │  gap: 16px between  │  cards             │   │
│  └─────────────────────┴────────────────────┘   │
│  Bottom Section (full width)                     │
└─────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
```

- **Content padding:** `24px 32px` (collapses to `16px` below 900px)
- **KPI grid:** `grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr)`, `gap: 12px`
- **Two-col grid:** `grid-template-columns: 60fr 40fr`, `gap: 16px`
- **Card vertical gap:** `margin-bottom: 16px` on each card (except last: `0`)

### Spacing Scale

| Value | Common usage |
|---|---|
| 3px | Badge vertical padding |
| 4px | Progress bar height; tag dot size |
| 5px | Icon gap in buttons/badges |
| 6px | Tag list gap; avatar text |
| 7px | Button padding (vertical); card head icon gap |
| 8px | Client action button gap |
| 9px | Badge radius fallback |
| 10px | Badge/tag horizontal padding |
| 12px | Activity row gap; client action gap; QA bar gap |
| 14px | Avatar–text gap; card head padding bottom; client row padding |
| 16px | Card body padding (vertical); card gap (grid); QA bar padding (horizontal) |
| 18px | Card body padding (horizontal); card head padding (horizontal) |
| 20px | Card head padding top |
| 24px | KPI card padding (horizontal) |
| 28px | Activity icon circle diameter |
| 32px | Header mobile padding |
| 40px | Client avatar diameter; nav item height |

