## 4. Component Specifications

### Card Container
```css
.card {
  background: var(--c-card);
  border: 1px solid var(--c-border);
  border-radius: calc(var(--radius) * 1.4);  /* ≈ 14px */
  box-shadow: var(--c-shadow);
  overflow: hidden;
  margin-bottom: 16px;
}
.card:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }
```

### Card Header (section title bar)
```css
.card-head {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 7px;
  padding: 14px 18px 12px;
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--c-border);
}
.card-head h3 {
  font-size: 11px;
  font-weight: 600;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  letter-spacing: 0.9px;
  color: var(--c-muted);
  font-family: var(--font-sans);
}
.card-head-icon { color: var(--c-muted); }  /* SVG icon, 13×13px, strokeWidth 2.5 */
```

### Card Body
```css
.card-body { padding: 16px 18px; }
```

---

### KPI Card
- **Grid:** 4 equal columns with `gap: 12px`
- **Internal layout:** `display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 14px`
- **Padding:** `16px 18px`
- **Border-radius:** `calc(var(--radius) * 1.4)` (same as .card)
- **Hover:** subtle green gradient overlay via `::before` pseudo-element (opacity 0 → 1)

```css
.kpi-card {
  background: var(--c-card);
  border: 1px solid var(--c-border);
  border-radius: calc(var(--radius) * 1.4);
  padding: 16px 18px;
  box-shadow: var(--c-shadow);
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 14px;
  position: relative;
  overflow: hidden;
}
.kpi-card::before {
  content: '';
  position: absolute;
  inset: 0;
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, oklch(0.98 0.01 163) 0%, transparent 60%);
  opacity: 0;
  transition: opacity 0.2s;
}
.kpi-card:hover::before { opacity: 1; }

.kpi-label {
  font-size: 11px;
  color: var(--c-muted);
  font-weight: 500;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  letter-spacing: 0.8px;
}
.kpi-value {
  font-size: 22px;
  font-weight: 600;
  font-family: var(--font-serif);
  line-height: 1.1;
  margin-top: 2px;
}
.kpi-sub {
  font-size: 11px;
  color: var(--c-muted);
  margin-top: 3px;
  font-family: var(--font-mono);
}
```

**KPI icon circles:** `width: 40px; height: 40px; border-radius: 50%`. Background is an `18%` opacity tint of the relevant accent color.

---

### Circular Progress
- **SVG-based**, `rotate(-90deg)` transform
- Track ring: `stroke: var(--c-border)`
- Fill ring: `stroke: var(--c-green)`, `stroke-linecap: round`
- Animation: `stroke-dashoffset` transitions with `1s cubic-bezier(.4, 0, .2, 1)`, triggered on mount with a 120ms delay

