### Status Badge (page-level, e.g. "Active")
```css
.status-badge {
  display: inline-flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 5px;
  padding: 3px 10px;
  border-radius: 20px;     /* full pill */
  font-size: 12px;
  font-weight: 500;
  letter-spacing: 0.2px;
  font-family: var(--font-sans);
}
/* Active variant */
.status-badge--active {
  background: var(--c-green-lt);
  color: var(--c-green);
}
.status-badge--active::before {
  content: '';
  width: 6px;
  height: 6px;
  border-radius: 50%;
  background: currentColor;
}
```

