### Buttons

**Default (ghost/outline):**
```css
.btn {
  display: inline-flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 6px;
  padding: 7px 14px;
  border-radius: var(--radius);
  font-size: 13px;
  font-weight: 500;
  font-family: var(--font-sans);
  border: 1px solid var(--c-border);
  background: var(--c-card);
  color: var(--c-text);
  cursor: pointer;
  transition: background 0.15s, border-color 0.15s, box-shadow 0.15s;
}
.btn:hover {
  background: var(--c-subtle);
  box-shadow: var(--c-shadow);
}
```

**Primary (filled green):**
```css
.btn-primary {
  background: var(--c-green);
  color: white;
  border-color: transparent;
}
.btn-primary:hover {
  background: var(--c-green-hover);
  box-shadow: 0 2px 8px oklch(0.60 0.13 163 / 30%);
}
```

**Destructive:**
```css
.btn-danger {
  color: var(--c-red);
  border-color: oklch(0.92 0.01 27);
}
.btn-danger:hover { background: oklch(0.98 0.01 27); }
```

**Small (client actions):**  `padding: 5px 12px; font-size: 12px`

