### Metric Grid (2-column inside cards)
```css
.metric-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
}
.metric {
  padding: 12px 0;
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--c-border);
}
/* Odd items get right border + padding */
.metric:nth-child(odd):not(:last-child) {
  padding-right: 16px;
  border-right: 1px solid var(--c-border);
}
.metric:nth-child(even) { padding-left: 16px; }
/* Remove bottom border from last row */
.metric:nth-last-child(-n+2) { border-bottom: none; padding-bottom: 0; }

.metric-label {
  font-size: 11px;
  color: var(--c-muted);
  font-weight: 500;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  letter-spacing: 0.6px;
}
.metric-value {
  font-size: 18px;
  font-weight: 600;
  font-family: var(--font-serif);
  margin-top: 3px;
}
.metric-sub {
  font-size: 11px;
  color: var(--c-muted);
  margin-top: 2px;
}
```

