### Mini Gantt Bar
```css
/* Track */
.gantt-track {
  position: relative;
  height: 8px;
  background: var(--c-border);
  border-radius: 4px;
}
/* Progress fill */
.gantt-fill {
  height: 100%;
  background: var(--c-green);
  border-radius: 4px;
  transition: width 1s cubic-bezier(.4, 0, .2, 1);
}
/* Today marker */
.gantt-marker {
  position: absolute;
  top: 50%;
  transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
  width: 14px;
  height: 14px;
  border-radius: 50%;
  background: var(--c-green);
  border: 2px solid white;
  box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px oklch(0.60 0.13 163 / 25%);
}
/* Date labels */
.gantt-labels {
  display: flex;
  justify-content: space-between;
  font-size: 11px;
  color: var(--c-muted);
  margin-bottom: 6px;
  font-family: var(--font-mono);
}
.gantt-today-label { color: var(--c-green); font-weight: 600; }
```

