## 7. Icons

- **Style:** Line/outline SVG, `strokeWidth: 2` (card head icons use `2.5`)
- **Card head icon size:** 13 × 13px
- **KPI icon size:** 18 × 18px, inside a 40px circle
- **Activity icon size:** 14 × 14px, inside a 28px circle
- **Button/inline icon size:** 14–16px
- No icon library required — inline SVG path data used throughout. Compatible with Lucide or Heroicons (outline) as drop-in equivalents.

