## 10. Data Visualization

### Circular Progress (SVG)
- Rendered with two `<circle>` elements on an SVG canvas
- Canvas rotated `-90deg` so fill starts from the top
- Track stroke: `var(--c-border)`; fill stroke: `var(--c-green)`
- Stroke linecap: `round`
- Animated via `stroke-dashoffset` on mount

### Sparkline (Time Burn — 7-day)
- 7 vertical bars, `height: 36px` container, `align-items: flex-end`
- Each bar: `flex: 1`, `border-radius: 2px 2px 0 0`, `opacity: 0.3`
- Empty state: `background: var(--c-border)`, `height: 4px` fixed
- Hover: `opacity: 0.8`
- Active bars: `background: var(--c-green)`

### Mini Gantt
- Single horizontal track (see component spec above)
- Date labels in `--font-mono`, 11px
- Today marker: 14px circle with `box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px oklch(0.60 0.13 163 / 25%)`

### Financial Health Metric — Profit Margin Bar
- 4px progress bar under the profit margin metric value
- Animates `width` from `0%` → actual `%` on mount
- Green if `profit_margin > 30`, amber otherwise

